{"name": "odoo-addon-mail-activity-plan", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-mail-activity-plan", "version": "16.0.1.0.1.2", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/social", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Mail activity plan", "upload_time": 1728016072}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fsocial-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/social\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/social/tree/16.0/mail_activity_plan\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/social-16-0/social-16-0-mail_activity_plan\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/social&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n  maintainer-victoralmau: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/victoralmau.png?size=40px\n    :alt: victoralmau\n    :target: https://github.com/victoralmau\n    ```\n---\n\n# Mail activity plan\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:fc80109d913a89acc0eb45c2d7ed9122baa654e52785ae70b439793e08289479\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module allows to define activity plans linked to any document type that allows to\nplan activities, and later launch them from the documents.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\nGo to *Settings > Technical > Discuss > Activity Plans* and create the ones you need\nlinked to a model (Contact for example).\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use this module, you need to:\n\n1. Go to a partner.\n2. Click on the 'Launch Activity Plan' button.\n3. Choose a plan.\n4. The \"Details\" tab will be displayed with a summary of the activities to be created.\n5. Click on the 'Create activities' button.\n6. Activities have been created in partner.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/social/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/social/issues/new?body=module:%20mail_activity_plan%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Tecnativa\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [Tecnativa](https://www.tecnativa.com):\n\n  - V\u00edctor Mart\u00ednez\n  - Pedro M. Baeza\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainer](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-victoralmau }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/social](https://github.com/OCA/social/tree/16.0/mail_activity_plan) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_plan.models", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_plan.models.mail_activity_plan", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_plan.models..mail_activity_plan", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_plan.models.mail_activity_plan", "documentation": ["Copyright 2024 Tecnativa - V\u00edctor Mart\u00ednez", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_plan.models.mail_activity_plan.MailActivityPlan", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_plan.models.mail_activity_plan.MailActivityPlan._compute_model", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_plan.models.mail_activity_plan.MailActivityPlan.get_total_plans_from_model", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "model", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_plan.models.mail_activity_plan.MailActivityPlan._get_plans_from_model", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "model", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_plan.models.mail_activity_plan.MailActivityPlan._name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mai